gw.api.builder

Class RenewalBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<PolicyPeriod,B>
      • gw.api.builder.JobBuilder<B>
        • gw.api.builder.NonSubmissionJobBuilder<RenewalBuilder>
          • gw.api.builder.RenewalBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExtendedMultiQuoteJobBuilder, IMultiQuoteJobBuilder, ValueGenerator<PolicyPeriod>

    public class RenewalBuilder
extends NonSubmissionJobBuilder<RenewalBuilder>
implements ExtendedMultiQuoteJobBuilder
    Builder for a renewal job. Simple usage is 
       new RenewalBuilder(basedOnPeriod).createAndCommit()
   new RenewalBuilder(basedOnPeriod).withAltBillingAccountNumber(newAccountNum).createAndCommit()
